## Attribution Guidelines

When using or building upon this work, please:

1. **Cite the project**: Use the citation information in CITATION.cff
2. **Provide a link**: https://collider-2031.com or https://github.com/murnanedaniel/ColliderLab
3. **Indicate modifications**: If you've made changes, note what was changed
4. **Maintain attribution**: Keep this license file and attribution in derivatives

